rows.label: bf10340100_0010
rows.name: Metsu!

rows.label: bf10340100_0020
rows.name:
Just in time for the show, kid!
These are the best seats in the house.

rows.label: bf10340100_0030
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10340100_0040
rows.name: Huh, I sound just like Yoshitsune there.

rows.label: bf10340100_0050
rows.name: Yoshitsune is dead, you know?

rows.label: bf10340100_0060
rows.name: So is Benkei... and Shin.

rows.label: bf10340100_0070
rows.name: Figured as much.

rows.label: bf10340100_0080
rows.name: ...Is that all?

rows.label: bf10340100_0090
rows.name:
What, you want me to cry and give a eulogy?
What's the point?

rows.label: bf10340100_0100
rows.name:
They wanted to disappear.
It's what they wished for.

rows.label: bf10340100_0110
rows.name: Then... I should just smile as I send them off...

rows.label: bf10340100_0120
rows.name: Metsu... is that really how you feel?

rows.label: bf10340100_0130
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf10340100_0140
rows.name: Is that your true feeling? Metsu.

rows.label: bf10340100_0150
rows.name: I don't understand what you're saying.

rows.label: bf10340100_0160
rows.name: You must realize it by now, right?

rows.label: bf10340100_0170
rows.name: That it's not your own will.

rows.label: bf10340100_0180
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf10340100_0190
rows.name: That it was implanted by Marveni.

rows.label: bf10340100_0200
rows.name: So what if it was?

rows.label: bf10340100_0210
rows.name: Don't give me that naive crap about repenting.

rows.label: bf10340100_0220
rows.name: What if I said that's exactly what I meant?

rows.label: bf10340100_0230
rows.name: ...In that case

rows.label: bf10340100_0235
rows.name: Don't mess with me, kid!

rows.label: bf10340100_0240
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!!

rows.label: bf10340100_0250
rows.name:
So Blades become Divine Beasts?
And Divine Beasts give life to humans...?

rows.label: bf10340100_0260
rows.name: Who cares about any of that?

rows.label: bf10340100_0270
rows.name: Things can be whatever they end up being.

rows.label: bf10340100_0280
rows.name: But... that man had lost everything.
